snippet.title: Can you solve this puzzle?
snippet.description:
Please push [LIKE] and [SUBSCRIBE] to Dobuki Gamer if you enjoyed watching me play!

-----------
. You think you can do better?

(... well I can hardly see how you cannot do better)

Try it out yourself on https://wot.dobuki.net/ 🎮

#Dobuki
